{"tid":93033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[強國] 為索\"喜錢\" 長者訓地包圍花車","createTime":"2017-01-24T05:52:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-24T07:38:08.000Z","uid":57376,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"161a5e11361d4235e1e7a9cb2dd23a3c03725409","tid":93033,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T05:52:20.000Z","msg":"內地傳媒昨日報道，安徽阜南一路口，21日有一部花車在燈位停車時，被一群長者攔截。他們向司機索取喜糖、喜煙和喜錢，圍着花車不肯離開，導致交通堵塞。最終經交警、行人勸說後，長者才給花車讓道。<br />\n<br />\n短片中所見，一群長者在花車團團包圍，警察到來還躺在車前，期間還發生肢體衝突。最終，<span style=\"color: red;\">司機還是無奈掏錢，眾人看到錢後一擁而上。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結婚本是喜慶事，攔車索取煙糖，過去只是發一支煙、一粒糖，而且全是認識的人一起起哄，而現在卻大不同，不管認識不認識，只要花車從村口經過，就有人上前阻攔，<span style=\"color: red;\">有人在路中間橫放一部私家車，有人放一些樹木，要煙是整條，利是一般要50元(人民幣‧下同)或100元</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，一趟娶親路，花費動輒數千元，給辦婚禮人帶來額外負擔。<br />\n<br />\n網民認為，要革除這種陋習，地方政府還得要大力整治，不能任其發展，陋習長期存在就會成為必然。"},{"pid":"2db6c79985eee71083053b8c629b18eb1089fcca","tid":93033,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T05:55:31.000Z","msg":"係我就大叫一句「落地開花，富貴榮華」<br />\n然後就轆過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c51b5cd2d213cb95f77acad19085f216276fb2a1","tid":93033,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T05:55:36.000Z","msg":"廢老，仲衰過狗。"},{"pid":"d239e7be81c57b60de1cf2259bc6f1b963bc044a","tid":93033,"uid":2521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T06:04:09.000Z","msg":"我朋友結婚係酒店出門<br />\n有D大陸旅客走黎同我R著數，話係大陸習俗<br />\n我即刻同佢講，依度係香港，香港係人地黎俾我地ge<br />\nD大陸人馬上四散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f27a2dc57268571a520264bef8f7f681f028bb75","tid":93033,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T06:04:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係我就大叫一句「落地開花，富貴榮華」<br />\n然後就轆過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇怕你餐酒, 都要喺赤柱擺啦。<br />\n到時唔洗比帖我, 我唔得閒。"},{"pid":"743de9d94e6abe7921a0e122353c7b3997c4544b","tid":93033,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T06:05:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我朋友結婚係酒店出門<br />\n有D大陸旅客走黎同我R著數，話係大陸習俗<br />\n我即刻同佢講，依度係香港，香港係人地黎俾我地ge<br />\nD大陸人馬上四散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2588c685351498d9bcfde1fb0be104cc2c6ccbe9","tid":93033,"uid":5455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T07:22:45.000Z","msg":"同打劫冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e6d24e446aa15e35c7c8e722773f5ce362c9396","tid":93033,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T07:34:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係我就大叫一句「落地開花，富貴榮華」<br />\n然後就轆過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇怕你餐酒, 都要喺赤柱擺啦。<br />\n到時唔洗比帖我, 我唔得閒。</blockquote><br />\n強國的話應該無咩事<br />\n比夠錢公安就得"},{"pid":"6110e357b1079437a356a57a7eb37d0413d37098","tid":93033,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T07:38:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我朋友結婚係酒店出門<br />\n有D大陸旅客走黎同我R著數，話係大陸習俗<br />\n我即刻同佢講，依度係香港，香港係人地黎俾我地ge<br />\nD大陸人馬上四散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}